  "time_ut": 1657698316,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Speaker action announcement about Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has left the country, Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardhana has made a special announcement.",
        "He said he has been informed that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe will assume the responsibility of the President in accordance with Article 37 of the Constitution."
      ],
